<Base title="SocialProof for Event Planners — Testimonials That Book More Events | SocialProof" description="Event planners: collect client testimonials that win your next booking. SocialProof helps you display authentic reviews on your website so couples and clients choose you with confidence.">
  <main>
    <section style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Social Proof for Event Planners
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Event planning is one of the highest-trust purchases a client makes. They're handing you a once-in-a-lifetime moment — a wedding, a milestone birthday, a corporate conference — and trusting you to execute it flawlessly. Before they sign anything, they read everything they can find about you. SocialProof helps you put your best client voices front and center, so that discovery process ends with them reaching out to you.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Why event planners live and die by testimonials</h2>
      <p>Photography shows what your events look like. Testimonials reveal what it actually felt like to work with you — how you handled the vendor who canceled at the last minute, how you soothed frayed nerves the morning of, how you made every guest feel the event was designed just for them. That's what converts a prospect into a client.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">SocialProof gives you an embeddable testimonial widget that sits beautifully on your website, turning every completed event into a permanent, working advertisement.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">What clients say when you've made their event perfect</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Stress elimination:</strong> "I didn't worry about a single thing the entire day. She handled everything — I just got to enjoy it."</li>
        <li><strong>Crisis management:</strong> "The florist canceled 48 hours out. She had a replacement by the next morning. I never even knew until after."</li>
        <li><strong>Detail obsession:</strong> "Every tiny detail I mentioned in passing ended up in the final event. She actually listened."</li>
        <li><strong>Vendor management:</strong> "Every vendor showed up, everything ran on schedule. That's not luck — that's her."</li>
        <li><strong>Personal touch:</strong> "Felt like planning with a friend who happened to know every vendor in the city."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How SocialProof works for your planning business</h2>
      <ol style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Embed the widget</strong> on your website — portfolio page, about page, or anywhere — in under 10 minutes.</li>
        <li><strong>Send the collection link</strong> a few days after the event, when the high is still real and the gratitude is fresh.</li>
        <li><strong>Review and approve</strong> testimonials before they go live — you stay in control.</li>
        <li><strong>Build your library</strong> event by event, until your website sells itself.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">The timing that gets heartfelt responses</h2>
      <p>Send your testimonial request 3–5 days after the event — not immediately, when clients are exhausted, and not weeks later, when the glow has faded. That sweet spot produces the kind of vivid, emotional testimonials that convert new prospects. Pair it with a personal note thanking them, and your response rate climbs dramatically.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Works for every event type</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li>Weddings and engagement parties</li>
        <li>Corporate events, conferences, and retreats</li>
        <li>Birthday and anniversary celebrations</li>
        <li>Baby and bridal showers</li>
        <li>Bar and bat mitzvahs</li>
        <li>Nonprofit galas and fundraisers</li>
        <li>Virtual and hybrid events</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Start free — no credit card required</h2>
      <p>SocialProof is free forever for one active widget. Start collecting testimonials from your last three events and watch your website start doing the selling for you.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" style="background:#0070f3;color:#fff;padding:.85rem 2rem;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;">Collect your first testimonial free →</a>
      </p>
    </section>
